ws and blocks</strong><br></li><li>army of enemies with <strong>unique behavior</strong> and combat moves<br></li><li>story-based adventure, featuring <strong>NPCs and quests</strong><br></li><li>fully voiced dialogues<br></li><li>open map to <strong>choose your path</strong><br></li><li><strong>loot system</strong> - weapons, armor and items to find, equip and use<br></li><li><strong>RPG system</strong> - combat moves, skills and perks to master<br></li><li>original soundtrack</li></ul>",
